  description: "Lai Ch\xE2u l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi thu\u1ED9c
    v\xF9ng T\xE2y B\u1EAFc B\u1ED9 \u1EDF ph\xEDa B\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam
    v\xE0 c\xF3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng bi\xEAn gi\u1EDBi gi\xE1p v\u1EDBi Trung Qu\u1ED1c.
    T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh ch\u1EE7 y\u1EBFu l\xE0 n\xFAi cao v\xE0
    nhi\u1EC1u d\xE3y n\xFAi h\xF9ng v\u0129, v\u1EDBi c\xE1c \u0111\u1ECBa danh
    n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt nh\u01B0 \u0110\u1EC9nh Pu Si Lung v\xE0 Cao nguy\xEAn S\xECn
    H\u1ED3, n\u01A1i c\xF3 kh\xED h\u1EADu m\xE1t m\u1EBB v\xE0 c\u1EA3nh quan thi\xEAn
    nhi\xEAn \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc.\n\nLai Ch\xE2u c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u s\u1EA3n v\u1EADt
    v\xE0 \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng nh\u01B0 Ch\xE8 shan
    tuy\u1EBFt, Th\u1ECBt tr\xE2u g\xE1c b\u1EBFp v\xE0 c\xE1c m\xF3n \u0103n ch\u1EBF
    bi\u1EBFn t\u1EEB m\u1EAFc kh\xE9n, lo\u1EA1i gia v\u1ECB \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng
    c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng n\xFAi T\xE2y B\u1EAFc.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, Lai Ch\xE2u
    l\xE0 n\u01A1i sinh s\u1ED1ng c\u1EE7a nhi\u1EC1u d\xE2n t\u1ED9c nh\u01B0 Th\xE1i,
    M\xF4ng, Dao, H\xE0 Nh\xEC v\u1EDBi b\u1EA3n s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a phong ph\xFA.
    C\xE1c l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng, trang ph\u1EE5c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c
    v\xE0 ch\u1EE3 phi\xEAn v\xF9ng cao th\u1EC3 hi\u1EC7n r\xF5 n\xE9t \u0111\u1EDDi
    s\u1ED1ng v\u0103n h\xF3a \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a c\u1ED9ng \u0111\u1ED3ng
    c\xE1c d\xE2n t\u1ED9c mi\u1EC1n n\xFAi T\xE2y B\u1EAFc."
